68 (22) "Respiratory Therapy," "Respiratory Therapy Practice," "Respiratory
69 Care," "the Practice of Respiratory Care," and "the Practice of Respiratory Therapy"
70 means the care and services provided by or under the direction and supervision of a
71 Respiratory Therapist or Respiratory Care Practitioner.
